high_descs: Turn around and head towards the stove on your right.
Pick up the pan on the right.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf inside the fridge.
Pick up the apple from inside the fridge.
Place the apple in the pan inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool apple inside a pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, then go straight, then turn right to face the oven.
Pick up the pot from the right side of the oven.
Turn around, then go straight to the fridge.
Put the pot on the top shelf of the fridge.
Pick up the apple from the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Place the apple in the pot on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple in a pot, in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front right burner of the stove.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge.
Pick up an apple from the fridge.
Put the apple in the pan.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple in a pan in the fridge.
